fields.title: Thor : Love and Thunder
fields.review: In Thor: Love and Thunder, the fourth movie dedicated to the blonde and beautiful Norse god, director Taika Waititi tries his best to resist those canine qualities from slobbering over his PG-13 rating.

fields.title: Crazy Rich Asian
fields.review: This movie was very entertaining. It was cool to see a mashup of romcom & party comedy to the backdrop of Chinese/Singapore culture & family traditions.

fields.title: How to Train Your Dragon
fields.review: The story is very engaging; there is nothing too sophisticated for kids and nothing too childish for adults.The characters are another strength. All the animations are spectacular!

fields.title: Candy Jar
